title: Lizzy Mercier Descloux - Press Color
description:
There is no genre suitable to describe this CD.

It&#039;s is a unique piece of work that emerged from the NY No Wave scene towards the ends of the 70s.

The vocals are sexy.
The bass is funky.
It&#039;s accessable & expirmental.

Have a listen.
